title: Synergy
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Organic, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic juice bar and cafe opened in spring 2013. One of the owner is a holistic nutrition and the other is a trained chef. Offers juices, smoothies, wheatgrass, sandwiches, wraps, and salads made with whole foods from local and regional farmers. The collard wraps are gluten-free. "No worries" atmosphere with Wi-Fi.
